name: $presentation
desc: Returns: The quantity of substance in the unit of presentation, or in the volume (or mass) of the single pharmaceutical product or manufactured item.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: The quantity of substance in the unit of presentation, or in the volume (or mass) of the single pharmaceutical product or manufactured item.

name: $presentationHighLimit
desc: Returns: An upper limit for the quantity of substance in the unit of presentation. For use when there is a range of strengths, this is the high limit, with the presentation attribute becoming the lower limit.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: An upper limit for the quantity of substance in the unit of presentation. For use when there is a range of strengths, this is the high limit, with the presentation attribute becoming the lower limit.

name: $concentration
desc: Returns: The strength per unitary volume (or mass).

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: The strength per unitary volume (or mass).

name: $concentrationHighLimit
desc: Returns: An upper limit for the strength per unitary volume (or mass), for when there is a range. The concentration attribute then becomes the lower limit.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: An upper limit for the strength per unitary volume (or mass), for when there is a range. The concentration attribute then becomes the lower limit.

desc: Returns: For when strength is measured at a particular point or distance.

pvardefs.desc: For when strength is measured at a particular point or distance.
